<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Card estilo notícia</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f2f2f2;
  }

  .card {
    width: 350px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 10px 10px rgba(1,0,1,0.1);
    margin: 20px auto;
  }
  .card :hover{
    transform: scale(1.02);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }

  .source {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .titulo {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #223;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .acao {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
  }

  .acao span {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.pcOK03d6_Emt4ymV6MA43gHaJN?w=203&h=252&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Imagem">

  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="source">Voce conhecia? • 1d </div>

    <div class="titulo">
      Países com as pessoas mais bonitas do mundo: A posição do Brasil 
    </div>

    <div class="acao">
      <span>👍 3.37k</span>
      <span>💬 167</span>
      <span>↗️ 67</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="card">
  <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.Wfp1IgmDGC6SOCS9cDKpCAHaEK?w=297&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Imagem">

  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="source">CNN Brasil • 3w </div>

    <div class="titulo">
      Após recusa do Iran em negociar, EUA anunciam sanções contra o país
    </div>

    <div class="acao">
      <span>👍 167.5k</span>
      <span>💬 1340</span>
      <span>↗️ 670</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
